Amazon Alexa and the KaBuM Smart products work together to to have a great experience of a connected home or office. See how simple it is to use voice control to turn on a light bulb just by talking to your Alexa Echo.

Just plug in your KaBuM! Smart ”with Alexa by following the steps below:

1) Download the app “KaBuM! Smart ”on the App Store (iOS) or Google Play (Android);
2) Create an account in the app by following the steps given;
3) Set up your smart device in the app and create a name for ease of use;
4) Download the Alexa app from the App Store (iOS) or Google Play (Android);
5) Set up your Echo device in the Alexa app;
6) Search for “KaBuM Smart” in Alexa> Skills
7) Tap Enable “KaBuM Smart”. You will be taken to an app login page;
8) Enter your account details (login and password);
9) Okay, now just ask Alexa and she will help you control your smart home.

Use simple phrases to control your devices. For example:

“Alexa, turn off the kitchen light”
“Alexa, turn on the room light”
